<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Airtel Thanks App - Quality Digital Services</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css"/>
  <style>
  * {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
}

body {
  background-color: #f2f4ff;
  padding: 20px;
}

.header {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  background-color: white;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
}

.logo {
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: bold;
}
.logo img {
  width: 300px;
  height: 80px;
}

.logo .highlight {
  color: #f57c00;
}

.nav-links a {
  margin: 0 10px;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: #f57c00;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.main-container {
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
  margin-top: 30px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.info-card {
  flex: 2;
  background-color: #e8f1ff;
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.info-card h2 {
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  color: #c60000;
}

.info-card h3 {
  margin-top: 20px;
  color: #333;
}

.info-card ul, .info-card ol {
  padding-left: 20px;
  margin-top: 10px;
}

.app-logo {
  width: 60px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.form-card {
  flex: 1;
  background-color: white;
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  border: 1px solid #ccc;
  box-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.form-card h2 {
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  text-align: center;
}

form {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}

label {
  margin: 10px 0 5px;
  font-weight: bold;
}

input, select {
  padding: 10px;
  border-radius: 5px;
  border: 1px solid #aaa;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.button {
  padding: 12px;
  background-color: #f57c00;
  color: white;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 5px;
  font-weight: bold;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background 0.3s;
}

.button:hover {
  background-color: #e06b00;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
 <header class="header">
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="image/Hiring_Poster1Artboard_8@4x[1](1).png"></div>
    <nav class="nav-links">
      <a href="/dashboard">Home</a>
      <a href="/aboutneed">About Us</a>
      <a href="/careerneed">Careers</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="main-container">
    <section class="info-card">
      <img src="image/SBI IRCTC Credit Card.png" alt="Airtel Logo" class="app-logo"/>
      <h2>SBI IRCTC Credit Card</h2>
      <li>India’s Favorite Card for Train Travelers</li>
      <h3>Key Benefits</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Save up to 10% Value Back on rail ticket purchases via IRCTC</li>
        <li>350 Bonus Reward Points on card activation</li>
        <li>Earn Reward Points every time you plan a trip</li>
        <li>1% waiver on transaction charges for bookings via [irctc.co.in](https://www.irctc.co.in)</li>
        <li>Applicable for AC1, AC2, AC3, and AC Chair Car ticket bookings</li>
       <li> Use IRCTC Mobile App (Android only) or website for maximum savings</li>
      </ul>
      <h3>How to Apply</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Click on Apply Now to start the application</li>
        <li>Fill in the required personal and financial details</li>
        <li>Submit the form and receive your application number</li>
        <li>Track your application using the reference number</li>
        <li>SBI Representative will contact you to complete verification and issuance process</li>
       
      </ul>
      <h3>who can apply?</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>Age: 21–65 years.</li>
        <li>Employment: Salaried or Self-employed</li>
        <li>Minimum Income: ₹20,000/month</li>
        <li> Credit Score: 700+ preferred</li>
        <li>Existing credit card holders are preferred</li>
        <li>Citizenship: Indian Citizens & NRIs</li>
      </ol>
      <h3>Terms & Conditions</h3>
      <ol>
      <li>Up to 10% value back on eligible IRCTC bookings</li>
      <li>Bonus Reward Points on joining section</li>
      <li> Offers applicable only on select booking classes and payment channels</li>
      <li>Reward earning & redemption policies are subject to change without notice</li>
      <li>Standard SBI Card terms & conditions apply</li>
      </ol>
      </ul>
    </section>

    
  </main>
<br><br>
  <a href="/CSIB" class="button" style="margin-left: 50%; text-decoration:none">Click Here To Continue</a>
  
</body>
</html>
